You should know what to expect from the Bring It On series.
They are predictable, light frivolous fun.
The first was by far the best film of the series, but the remaining 4 films aren't too bad.

This is a great way to enjoy the entire Bring It On series. The movies aren't the most high-quality films you'll ever find, but we all know that we are't watching for quality, we're watching because its fun. If you like cheerleading, you'll like these movies. And if you're not too into cheering, it's still a fun sleepover series to enjoy with friends.
